 Agriculture and Water Resources Minister Alhaji Mohammed Nanono comes face to face with Kebbi overwhelming flood at Dukku Community along Nigeria-Niger highway and washes his hands in the flood with Kebbi Governor, Abubakar Atiku Bagudu, by the side.  Vanguard News  Kebbi Government on Tuesday confirmed the death of a soldier and nine others in two separate flood disasters across the state. September 4, 2018 In "News" The Federal Government has distributed 149 trucks of fertiliser and agricultural inputs to 11,345 victims of the 2018 flood in Kebbi. October 25, 2019 In "News" The Kebbi Government is partnering the World Fish Programme to boost the fisheries potentials of the State. October 9, 2019 In "Agric"